title: 147 - Truck Wars
description: Today's episode is hosted by Nick Maraldo and jumps right into a catch up of what the boys have been up to lately. There is no update on Mitt's apartment scam as expected. The boys catch up on all of their latest shows and then jump right into the "Pod Fod". Todays episode consists of an update on the Bill vs. Tony truck wars, tractor Zeet, "football fish", and much more from all around the internet. Make sure to subscribe and watch at youtube.com/thepodpmi and send in your submission into the Pod Fod @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. we appreciate you all for following along and well see you Friday.
